OL,3,CVillagers say 'stadium-sized'
OL,4,Cwarehouse has devalued their homes
OL,6,FResidents living in the rural village
OL,7,Fof Pilning in South Gloucestershire
OL,8,Fsay a new 'stadium-size' warehouse
OL,9,Fbeing built nearby has devalued their
OL,10,Fhomes and ruined the area.
OL,12,FMany claim they were not warned about
OL,13,Fthe sheer scale of the new development
OL,14,Fwhich is more than half a million
OL,15,Fsquare feet and has been nicknamed
OL,16,Flocally as 'the mega-shed'.
