OL,3,CVillagers say 'stadium-sized'
OL,4,Cwarehouse has devalued their homes
OL,6,FSouth Gloucestershire Council said
OL,7,Fthey had 'limited' control to exercise
OL,8,Fover the project due to historic
OL,9,Fplanning permission for the Severnside
OL,10,Farea granted in 1957.
OL,12,FSue Jones who has lived in Pilning for
OL,13,Fnearly 30 years said the new
OL,14,Fdevelopment was 'disgraceful'.
OL,16,FShe said: "How have they been allowed
OL,17,Fto build it so close to our
OL,18,Fproperties? It's made everything dark,
OL,19,Fthe constant noise and dust. There was
OL,20,Fno advertisement or warning. It was
OL,21,Fall clandestine."
