OL,3,CVillagers say 'stadium-sized'
OL,4,Cwarehouse has devalued their homes
OL,6,FResident Nick Gannon added: "It's just
OL,7,Fso big and so impactful and affecting
OL,8,Fpeople's lives. The issue is, it seems
OL,9,Fthere's nothing we can do about it."
OL,11,FMeanwhile Simone Harrison-Kelly
OL,12,Fdescribed the change in her beautiful
OL,13,Fviews as "quite horrific", making her
OL,14,Fre-consider living in the area.
OL,16,FThe councillor for Pilning, who
OL,17,Fobjected to the warehouse's
OL,18,Fconstruction, explained that historic
OL,19,Fplanning permission has allowed this
OL,20,F500,000 sq ft structure to be built.
