OL,3,CVillagers say 'stadium-sized'
OL,4,Cwarehouse has devalued their homes
OL,6,FCllr Simon Johnson said: "It goes back
OL,7,Fto a historic planning consent in the
OL,8,F1950s. Probably for the best will in
OL,9,Fthe world after the Second World War a
OL,10,Frebuilding mission was on track there.
OL,12,F"But what we're now seeing here in
OL,13,F2025 and what's being built on these
OL,14,Fblanket planning consents no longer
OL,15,Ffit for purpose.
OL,17,F"This should not have been built at
OL,18,Fthis height and not with this much
OL,19,Fimpact for local residents."
