OL,3,CVillagers say 'stadium-sized'
OL,4,Cwarehouse has devalued their homes
OL,6,FClaire Young MP, Liberal Democrat for
OL,7,FPilning and Yate, has raised the issue
OL,8,Fin parliament and is calling for a
OL,9,Fdebate in front of ministers.
OL,11,FClaire Young MP said: "Historic
OL,12,Fconsents need to be looked at and we
OL,13,Fneed legislation to introduce modern
OL,14,Fconditions on them, so we don't have
OL,15,Fthis situation where people's very
OL,16,Freasonable concerns can't be taken
OL,17,Finto consideration.
OL,26,@sD@WOU
