OL,3,CVillagers say 'stadium-sized'
OL,4,Cwarehouse has devalued their homes
OL,6,F"In the early 90s the government
OL,7,Fregularized this for quarries but they
OL,8,Fdidn't fix ones like this (Severnside)
OL,9,Fconsent. Now I'm asking them to finish
OL,10,Fthe job and that's why I'm calling for
OL,11,Fa debate to directly ask ministers."
OL,13,FA Government spokesperson said: "We're
OL,14,Ftaking decisive action to update the
OL,15,Fplanning system and get Britain
OL,16,Fbuilding, while ensuring communities
OL,17,Fare engaged with developers' plans.
