OL,6,F"Councils are ultimately responsible
OL,7,Ffor reviewing old permissions if the
OL,8,Fdevelopment is no longer suitable and
OL,9,Fdeciding whether action is necessary."
OL,11,FIn a statement, South Gloucestershire
OL,12,FCouncil explained they had limited
OL,13,Fpowers to halt the project.
