OL,6,FA spokesperson for South
OL,7,FGloucestershire Council, said: "Much
OL,8,Fof the new development at Severnside
OL,9,Fis governed by a planning permission
OL,10,Fgranted in 1957, pre-dating both South
OL,11,FGloucestershire Council and probably
OL,12,Fthe arrival of many local residents in
OL,13,FEaster Compton. This permission gives
OL,14,Fwide ranging powers for development
OL,15,Fwith limited remaining control for the
OL,16,Fcouncil to exercise."
